#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: C/objective.page:24
msgid ""
"To earn points in 2048, you need to combine squares with the same numerical "
"label. This is done by shifting the board in a direction in which two "
"equivalent squares meet. If the board is full and you cannot combine any "
"squares, the game ends."
msgstr ""
"在 2048 中，要获得分数，您需要合并带有相同数字的方块。操作方法是向某个方向滑"
"动棋盘，使两个相同数字的方块相遇。如果棋盘已满且无法再合并任何方块，那么游戏"
"结束"

#. (itstool) path: info/desc
#: C/controls.page:16
msgid "Default controls for <app>2048</app>"
msgstr "<app>2048</app> 默认控制方式"

#. (itstool) path: page/title
#: C/controls.page:19
msgid "Controls"
msgstr "控制方式"

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: C/controls.page:21
msgid ""
"You can click and drag your mouse on the board to shift squares in the same "
"direction. If you want to use the keyboard instead, the default keys to "
"shift the squares in <app>2048</app> are:"
msgstr ""
"您可以在棋盘上单击并拖动鼠标，向同一方向移动方块。如果您想改用键盘，在 "
"<app>2048</app> 中移动方块的默认按键如下:"

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/controls.page:25
msgid "<key>←</key> to shift squares left."
msgstr "<key>←</key> 向左移动方块。"

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/controls.page:28
msgid "<key>↑</key> to shift squares up."
msgstr "<key>↑</key> 向上移动方块。"

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/controls.page:31
msgid "<key>→</key> to shift squares right."
msgstr "<key>→</key> 向右移动方块。"

#. (itstool) path: item/p
#: C/controls.page:34
msgid "<key>↓</key> to shift squares down."
msgstr "<key>↓</key> 向下移动方块。"

#. (itstool) path: info/desc
#: C/scores.page:16
msgid "View high scores in <app>2048</app>"
msgstr "查看 <app>2048</app> 的最高分"

#. (itstool) path: page/title
#: C/scores.page:19
msgid "Viewing high scores"
msgstr "查看高分"

#. (itstool) path: page/p
#: C/scores.page:21
msgid ""
"Select the menu button on the top right corner or press <key>F10</key> and "
"then select <gui style=\"button\">Scores</gui> to view high scores. Open the "
"menu labelled \"Grid Size\" to select the grid size to view high scores for."
msgstr ""
"点击右上角的菜单按钮，或按 <key>F10</key>，然后选择 <gui style=\"button\">高"
"分</gui> 即可查看最高分。打开标有“网格尺寸”的菜单，选择要查看最高分的网格尺"
"寸。"

